   functionally conserved. Although neither approach yields an unambiguous
   root to the tree, both approaches strongly indicate that the root of bee
   phylogeny does not fall near Colletidae, as has been previously
   proposed. We discuss paralog rooting as a general strategy and why this
   approach performs relatively poorly with our particular dataset.
