Abstract = {{Osmia lignaria Say (Hymenoptera: Megachilidae) can be used to pollinate
   fruit trees. Populations are sometimes difficult to sustain because some
   female bees fail to establish at provided nesting sites. We address the
   hypothesis that rough handling of overwintered O. lignaria results in
