   Engel; and E. (E.) perpulchra Moure and Schlindwein. Euglossa
   meliponoides Ducke and E. urarina Hinojosa-Diaz and Engel are newly
   synonymized under E. decorata, E. decorata ruficauda Cockerell is
   synonymized under E. singularis, and a neotype is designated for E.
