   bees and 13 wasps) and 49 visited plants, with a connectance of 15.34\%.
   The wasp-plant network had higher connectance (C = 21.24) than the
   bee-plant network (C = 15.79). Both the social wasp-plant and the social
   bee-plant network were significantly nested, they presented structure
   more nested than all randomly generated matrices (n = 1 000). Both
   interaction networks have similar topologies and are nested,
